{"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC14","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Accessibility on iOS"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"iOS offers unmatched accessibility support that can help you reach a wider audience. Join us for an exploration of the features that iOS offers for users with specific needs, in areas such as vision, hearing, movement, and learning. Learn how to leverage existing and new UIAccessibility APIs in iOS 8, including expanded support for low vision users, to ensure that your app’s features are available to all users."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc14-210-accessibility-on-ios"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"article","sections":[],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2014\/210\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14-210-Accessibility-on-iOS"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14"]]},"references":{"WWDC14-Icon.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14-Icon.png"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC14-Icon.png","type":"image"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{